features.text:
##This is a free event, no paid sponsorships. I threw this event for the betterment of the entire crypto art community. I hope you enjoy your time here and possibly buy some art. If you feel like supporting this event, please drop a satoshi or ether and it will be used for future shows.

##- Coldie

#Over 50 artists featured in this 3 building exhibit

###Special thanks to everyone who helped make this show a reality including...

#Ben Nolan, Async, Super Rare, Avastars, Cointelegraph Magazine, Josie, Matt Kane, JOY, Crypto Motors, Myph-Space, Chief Monkey, JamesSW, n0shot, Bullauge333, trippyogi, Brookehawk, tommy, nissla, ross, javo + many more in CV community

##Enjoy your stay and take home some digital and physical art. 100% goes to the artists.
##Celebrating the art of Bitcoin and decentralization, Citadel 6.15 has opened its doors for a rare chance inside for all, no matter if you have 6.15 Bitcoin or not.

#How to buy art

###Click on images to find out details. Click the BID button below to bid/buy. Digital art is mostly Ethereum-based. Buyers must have an Ethereum wallets to purchase digital art.

###Physical art can be purchased directly by visiting the artist's website by clicking links below art. Physical art has a blue label next to it.

##If you don't have cryptocurrency to buy art digitally, reach out direct to artists!
GET OUT WHILE YOU STAY IN

#Who is Coldie?

Coldie is an award-winning mixed media artist whose stereoscopic 3D art has been featured in national juried art exhibitions in the United States. Creating art that has deeper meaning and symbolism interweaves form and function into the art he makes. His blockchain themed artwork including the 'Decentral Eyes' portrait series gives a personalized visual representation of the disruptive industry. Buyers of his 3D art can redeem a free pair of 3D glasses from the artist for 3D depth experience.
